quran[29{c,v,t}:
37,154,Maa lakum kaifa tahkumoon
37,155,Afalaa tazakkaroon
37,156,Am lakum sultaanum mubeen
37,157,Faatoo bi Kitaabikum in kuntum saadiqeen
37,158,Wa ja'aloo bainahoo wa bainal jinnati nasabaa; wa laqad 'alimatil jinnatu innahum lamuhdaroon
37,159,Subhaanal laahi 'ammaa yasifoon
37,160,Illaa 'ibaadal laahil mukhlaseen
37,161,Fa innakum wa maa ta'ubdoon
37,162,Maaa antum 'alaihi befaaatineen
37,163,Illaa man huwa saalil jaheem
37,164,Wa maa minnasa illaa lahoo maqaamum ma'loom
37,165,Wa innaa llanah nus saaffoon
37,166,Wa innaa lanah nul musabbihoon
37,167,Wa in kaanoo la yaqooloon
37,168,Law anna 'indana zikram minal awwaleen
37,169,Lakunna 'ibaadal laahil mukhlaseen
37,170,Fakafaroo bihee fasawfa ya'lamoon
37,171,Wa laqad sabaqat Kalimatunaa li'ibaadinal mursa leen
37,172,Innaa hum lahumul mansooroon
37,173,Wa inna jundana lahumul ghaaliboon
37,174,Fatawalla 'anhum hatta heen
37,175,Wa absirhum fasawfa yubsiroon
37,176,Afabi'azaabinaa yasta'jiloon
37,177,Fa izaa nazala bisaahatihim fasaaa'a sabaahul munzareen
37,178,Wa tawalla 'anhum hattaa heen
37,179,Wa absir fasawfa yubsiroon
37,180,Subhaana Rabbika Rabbil 'izzati 'amma yasifoon
37,181,Wa salaamun 'alalmursaleen
37,182,Walhamdu lillaahi Rabbil 'aalameen�(section 5)
